Reflex - Circle Timing Game
A simple and fast-paced reaction game built with React and TailwindCSS. Click at the right moment when the rotating circle enters the target zone to score.

Features
- Clean, responsive UI
- Fast visual feedback
- Animated circle and hit zone
- Scoring system based on precision

Getting Started
Install dependencies:
bash
npm install
Run the development server:
bash
Copy
Edit
npm run dev
Build for production:
bash
Copy
Edit
npm run build
Tech Stack
Vite + React 
